pd_0_com_0text: Well, you don’t look very good.
pd_3_com_0text: What.. aren’t you going to help me?
pd_4_com_0text: I’m tremendous pain. Could you help me.
pd_5_com_0text: I’m sorry but I don’t like blood. Good luck though.
pd_7_com_0text: Well. I would say the same but I don’t have to hope anymore, do I?
pd_8_com_0text: I understand what you are saying.(Kill)
pd_8_com_1text: How do you want me to help?
pd_11_com_0text: No no no… not what I meant.
pd_12_com_0text: No man should suffer like this. Don’t worry it will be over soon.
pd_14_com_0text: I have a healing potion in my bag.
pd_15_com_0text: Will you apply it to my wound?
pd_18_com_0text: Thanks, it feels already way better.
pd_19_com_0text: You saved my life. Thank you so much.
pd_21_com_0text: I will never hunt again. I can say you that.
pd_22_com_0text: Hunting? Were you the prey or something?
